These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, milk, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, sailing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is not the person drinking milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | 7up    | almond-milk    | milk |
| Sport      | swimming | rugby | sailing | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, 7up, water
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, pumpkin, avocado, plum
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
4. the person drinking juice is not the person eating pumpkin##6
5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice  | 7up    | soy-milk | water    |
| Food       | plum | pumpkin | avocado  | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, 7up, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, security-guard, librarian, entrepreneur
1. the person drinking soy-milk is not the dancer##6
2. the security-guard is not the person drinking 7up##6
3. the librarian is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
4. the security-guard is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the security-guard##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
7. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | coffee  | iced-tea  | 7up |
| Job        | librarian | entrepreneur | security-guard | dancer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, frog, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, scooter, van
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person driving the van is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | frog | lizard     | dog |
| Transport   | airplane     | scooter    | snowmobile | van    |

