.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, sprite, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, scooter, quad-bike, train
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person driving the train##6
5. the person driving the van is not the person drinking juice##6
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | juice        | lemonade | sprite | cola |
| Transport   | train | van | scooter     | quad-bike   |

