.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, romance, sports, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, american, chinese, brazilian
1. the japanese is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is not the american##6
3. the japanese is on the far right##1
4. the american is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
5. the person watching sports movies is the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
7. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
8. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
9. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | sports    | family  | epic   |
| Nationality   | chinese  | brazilian | american | japanese |

