.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, romance, mystery, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, trance, electronic
1. the fan trance is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
2. the fan trance is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the person watching horror movies is the fan salsa##1
4. the fan jazz is on the left or right of the fan electronic##3
5. the fan trance is on the far left##1
6. the person watching romance movies is the fan jazz##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | romance     | mystery | horror |
| Music-Genre   | trance | jazz | electronic      | salsa         |

