.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, fisherman, pilot, dressmaker
1. the lawyer is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
6. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
7. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
8. the person drinking fanta is not the dressmaker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | fanta  | cola        | hot-chocolate      | almond-milk          |
| Job        | lawyer | fisherman | dressmaker | pilot |

