.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, accountant, coach, entrepreneur
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, scooter, jet-ski
1. the project-manager is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the quad-bike is not the entrepreneur##6
3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the coach##1
7. the project-manager is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
8. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | project-manager  | coach | entrepreneur    | accountant |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | scooter | boat  |

