.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, hamster, dog, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is soccer is not the owner of the horse##6
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the owner of the dog is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
6. the person who's sport is cycling is not the owner of the hamster##6
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the dog is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | dog | horse        | chinchilla  | hamster     |
| Sport   | soccer     | skateboarding | cycling | lacrosse |

