.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, filmmaking, cooking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, rock, gospel
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
2. the fan reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
3. the fan rock is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the fan gospel and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the fan reggae is between the fan salsa and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | collecting    | card-games | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | reggae | gospel   | rock     |

