2. the person eating nectarine is not the person driving the helicopter##6
3. the person driving the subway is the person eating nectarine##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating kale##1
5. the person driving the boat is not the person eating nectarine##6
6. the person eating kale is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
8. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | potato  | peach | kale | nectarine |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter     | jet-ski     | subway    |

