.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, writing, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, rabbit, bird
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the bird is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
5. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | hiking | writing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Pet     | rabbit  | guinea-pig      | hamster  | bird       |

