2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the subway is not the person drinking tea##6
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the person driving the train is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | tea | cola | 7up      | coffee   |
| Transport   | airplane  | train   | motorbike | subway |

 